Stdlib-only Python; no deps.
Exit codes: 0=GREEN / 1=YELLOW / 2=RED.
Flags: \[en]strict requires state=ok everywhere; \[en]json for
machine-readable triage.
See scripts/diagnostics/ms022-doctor.py \[en]help for the full flag
